<P>
MARY PICKFORD CENTER DEDICATED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Actor Buddy Rogers was at the Gene Autry Western Heritage Museum in Griffith 
Park Wednesday to dedicate the Mary Pickford Education Center and Library. The 
center has three classrooms, a docent library and the administrative complex 
for the Western museum's education department. 
