<HEADLINE>
<P>
EDBERG, GILBERT WIN; MUSTER ELIMINATED BY MANSDORF 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By AP 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
SCOTTSDALE, Ariz. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Second-seeded Stefan Edberg of Sweden and sixth-seeded Brad Gilbert won their 
second-round matches in contrasting fashion Wednesday, while fourth-seeded 
Thomas Muster of Austria was eliminated by unseeded Amos Mansdorf in the 
$415,000 Eagle tennis tournament. 
</P>
<P>
