<P>
Profile 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA030989-0168 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 28664 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
March 9, 1989, Thursday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part 5; Page 14; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
